rComments: Pat is very knowledgable about Calculus/ math in general and is MORE than willing to meet outside of class to help students understand. He is very personable as well. Tests are quite reasonable, homework is optional (except for 2-3 mandatory assignments), and Pat is pretty funny at times. There's really nothing negative to say. Pa was great.
Easy quizzes and tests.  But the class material itself is pretty difficult.  So be aware!
